name: TLPS
description: TLPS, June 3 - July 9, 2021.Lydian Stater is excited to present TLPS, an exhibition featuring first-ever NFT works from eleven artists: Jeffrey Michael Austin, Marcos Castro, Matthew Cronin, Yi Hsuan Lai, Marta Rodriguez Maleck & Zac Manuel, Cedric Tai, Anika Todd, Catalina Tuca, Victor Yañez-Lazcano, and Alisa Yang. www.lydianstater.co
